 Wicked: Ordinary foes might win my mercy, but my sworn enemies do not.\n\n- By Any Means Necessary: My qualms can\u0027t get in the way of exterminating my foes.\n\n- Restitution: If my foes wreak ruin on the world, it is because I failed to stop them. I must help those harmed by their misdeeds","level":3}],"id":"Custom73df4907-4cfd-4b63-a633-04dc4801cd71","isFeature":true,"jsonType":"feat","level":1,"name":"Tenets of Vengeance","notes":"","type":"Feat"},"level":3},{"feat":{"descriptionModels":[{"description":"3rd \t--\u003e Bane, Hunter\u0027s Mark","level":3},{"description":"3rd \t--\u003e Bane, Hunter\u0027s Mark\n5th \t--\u003e Hold Person, Misty Step","level":5},{"description":"3rd \t--\u003e Bane, Hunter\u0027s Mark\n5th \t--\u003e Hold Person, Misty Step\n9th \t--\u003e Haste, Protection from Energy","level":9},{"description":"3rd \t--\u003e Bane, Hunter\u0027s Mark\n5th \t--\u003e Hold Person, Misty Step\n9th \t--\u003e Haste, Protection from Energy\n13th\t--\u003e Banishment, Dimension Door","level":13},{"description":"3rd \t--\u003e Bane, Hunter\u0027s Mark\n5th \t--\u003e Hold Person, Misty Step\n9th \t--\u003e Haste, Protection from Energy\n13th\t--\u003e Banishment, Dimension Door\n17th\t--\u003e Hold Monster, Scrying","level":17}],"id":"Customcfe108b2-edd2-4212-b3f1-8f6b8c2ec3c8","isFeature":true,"jsonType":"feat","level":1,"name":"Oath of Vengeance Spells","notes":"","type":"Feat"},"level":3},{"feat":{"descriptionModels":[{"description":"You gain the following two Channel Divinity options.\n\n- Abjure Enemy: As an action, choose one creature within 60 feet of you that you can see. That creature must make a Wisdom saving throw, unless it is immune to being frightened. Fiends and undead have disadvantage on this saving throw. On a failed save, the creature is frightened for 1 minute or until It takes any damage. While frightened,the creature\u0027s speed is 0, and It can\u0027t benefit from any bonus to its speed. On a successful save, the creature\u0027s speed is halved for 1 minute or until the creature takes any damage.\n\n- Vow of Enmity: As a bonus action, you can utter a vow of enmity against a creature you can see within 10 feet of you. You gain advantage on attack rolls against the creature for 1 minute or until it drops to 0 hit points or falls unconscious","level":3}],"id":"Customb33d99a9-b99e-4fb7-a827-5006a06c0850","isFeature":true,"jsonType":"feat","level":1,"name":"Channel Divinity","notes":"","type":"Feat"},"level":3},{"feat":{"descriptionModels":[{"description":"When you hit a creature with an opportunity attack, you can move up to half your speed immediately after the attack and as part of the same reaction. This movement doesn\u0027t provoke opportunity attacks","level":7}],"id":"Custom50b4631b-a7e8-4a51-a392-666365d2d80d","isFeature":true,"jsonType":"feat","level":1,"name":"Relentless Avenger","notes":"","type":"Feat"},"level":7},{"feat":{"descriptionModels":[{"description":"When a creature under the effect of your Vow of Enmity makes an attack, you can use your reaction to make a melee weapon attack against that creature if it is within range","level":15}],"id":"Custom66d570cf-72fa-440f-8de3-0cdec365772a","isFeature":true,"jsonType":"feat","level":1,"name":"Soul of Vengeance","notes":"","type":"Feat"},"level":15},{"feat":{"descriptionModels":[{"description":"Using your action, you undergo a transformation.\n\nFor 1 hour, you gain the following benefits:\n\nWings sprout from your back and grant you a flying speed of 60 feet.\nYou emanate an aura of menace in a 30-foot radius. The first time any enemy creature enters the aura or starts its turn there during a battle, the creature must succeeded on a Wisdom saving throw or become frightened of you for 1 minute or until it takes any damage. Attack rolls against the frightened creature have advantage.\nOnce you use this feature, you can\u0027t use it again until you finish a long rest","level":20}],"id":"Custombd82dd77-ad38-418e-895f-0b3659983ab9",