se it again until the start of your next turn","level":7}],"id":"Custom166ed0c5-2dd4-4ea1-8599-3e4c266888c8","isFeature":true,"jsonType":"feat","level":1,"name":"Mighty Deed","notes":"","type":"Feat"},"level":7},{"feat":{"descriptionModels":[{"description":"Your blessed glory on the battlefield can misdirect an attack. When a creature you can see hits you with an attack roll, you can use your reaction to gain a bonus to AC against that attack, potentially causing it to miss you. The bonus equals your Charisma modifier (minimum of +1). If the attack misses, you can make one weapon attack against the attacker as part of this reaction","level":15}],"id":"Custom594fb97f-7fc2-4f8b-b114-16647daf2f71","isFeature":true,"jsonType":"feat","level":1,"name":"Glorious Defense","notes":"","type":"Feat"},"level":15},{"feat":{"descriptionModels":[{"description":"You can now empower yourself with the legendsâ€”whether true or exaggeratedâ€”told of your great deeds. As a bonus action, you gain the following benefits for 10 minutes:\n\n- You are blessed with otherworldly comeliness, gaining advantage on all Charisma checks.\n\n- Once on each of your turns when you make a weapon attack and miss, you can cause that attack to hit instead.\n\n- If you fail a saving throw, you can use your reaction to succeed instead.\n\nOnce you use this feature, you canâ€™t use it again until you finish a long rest","level":20}],"id":"Custom9dd62af6-10c8-494c-babe-c1da2caef4df","isFeature":true,"jsonType":"feat","level":1,"name":"Living Myth","notes":"","type":"Feat"},"level":20}],"hpModifier":"Constitution","id":"paladin_oath_of_heroism_[ua]","jsonType":"class","languages":[],"modelType":"Archetype","multiclassArmor":true,"multiclassSkills":true,"multiclassTools":true,"multiclassWeapons":true,"name":"Oath of Heroism [UA]","selectableFeatures":[],"shouldShowCompanion":false,"skillProficiencies":[],"specialAbilities":[],"spellSlots":[],"spellcastingAbility":"Charisma","spells":[{"level":3,"spellModel":{"c